  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In newborn infants submitted to surgical procedures, tramadol may provide an effective
      analgesia and decrease the time on mechanical ventilation support and the time to achieve
      full enteral feeding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
